		"rawItemType": 9,
		"itemType": "Review",
		"reviewID": 686756,
		"rating": 5,
		"text": "As a Tiramisu-Lover, I decided to try this recipe, based on the reviews.  The only thing I can say is WOW!!!!  The RICH & CREAMY flavor mixed with the Coffee-soaked lady fingers leaves you wanting more!  VERY IMPORTANT: Let it refrigerate AT LEAST 24 hours; the flavors really need to blend!! I tasted the mixture right after adding the Marscapone Cheese and it tasted very bland.  However, after refrigerating overnight, it was probably better than any Tiramisu I'd ever tasted.  ONE MORE IMPORTANT TIP: As others have mentioned, doubling the coffee / rum mixture is a MUST.  You get that espresso taste, blended with the creamy flavor - HEAVENLY!",
		"dateLastModified": "2006-04-04T03:27:09.56",
